Varnish Administration GUI

* VCL Editor
* Purge

Varnish 3.X 4.X

Varnish VCL:

acl purge {
    "localhost";
    "0.0.0.0"/0;
}

----- vcl_recv

    if (req.request == "PURGE") {
        if (!client.ip ~purge) {
            error 405 "Not allowed";
        }
        ban("req.http.host == " +req.http.host+" && req.url ~ "+req.url);
        error 200 "Ban added";
    }

